title: Kurt Seligmann Exotic Garden Tote and Umbrella Set
description:
Tote and Umbrella developed from Kurt Seligmann’s Exotic garden, 1954, from The Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

The ethereal botanicals grace our umbrella and tote.  Warm colors and enchanting imagery provide shelter, convenience and style; a true benefit on a dreary day.

  • Dimensions: Closed- 11 x 2 in.  Open – 36 in.
  • Materials: Polyester
  • Auto open, close.
  • Storage sleeve for umbrella included.
